name: qualimap

variants.name: build_system
variants.description: Build systems supported by the package

description:
Qualimap 2 is a platform-independent application written in Java and R
that provides both a Graphical User Inteface (GUI) and a command-line
interface to facilitate the quality control of alignment sequencing data
and its derivatives like feature counts.

dependencies.name: java
dependencies.description:
The Java Development Kit (JDK) released by Oracle Corporation in the
form of a binary product aimed at Java developers. Includes a complete
JRE plus tools for developing, debugging, and monitoring Java
applications.
